e099380669","tid":1102490,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:13:24.000Z","msg":"台灣應該都幾難比中國統一, 有咩事發生可能會比美國鎮壓"},{"pid":"309812d000448f2960f976839e1b3c52763a070c","tid":1102490,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:28:36.000Z","msg":"當年日本大地震引發海嘯，再加上福島核能電廠危機未解， 各國爆發撤僑風潮。美國將大批僑民撤到無邦交台灣，而唔係南韓 中國 菲律賓 關島等。"},{"pid":"409592541a1a52f55ef4e816eafbf536a0d1437d","tid":1102490,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"講到咁明<br />\n成地玻璃碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f14ff1215831df16c7c79c56bec7420ebf0d296","tid":1102490,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得好似捉圍棋啲&quot;雙活&quot;咁<br />\n萬一支那眞係發神經收返台灣<br />\n又或者台灣真係話立國<br />\n咁就等仆街冚家剷啦"},{"pid":"75c0cc2b2d0e2016804116af7fb2a822c863297d","tid":1102490,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"好正，篇野激死班支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c756c71c6d391ce3484129928c3d7c065cafc4e1","tid":1102490,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eea826801e9cce2fdb60d1d3de1a9438a122eaf0","tid":1102490,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"eecef51c2e634122c230486c9dc82423bdd3aa7f","tid":1102490,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"15b0029b5607bd3dd241e9c5732e8f162ed79375","tid":1102490,"uid":237562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T23:41:25.000Z","msg":"好在有李登輝先生咋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T00:09:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T00:25:33.000Z","msg":"民進黨係柒<br />\n但主權唔係自己度"},"citedBy":1,"reply